## Set background color: `element_rect()`

::: {.tiny-font}


::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code}
ggplot(penguins) +
  aes(flipper_length_mm, body_mass_g) +
  geom_point(aes(color = species)) +
  theme_minimal_grid() +
  theme(
    plot.background = element_rect(
      fill = "aliceblue"
    )
  )
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![&nbsp;](figure-design_files/figure-revealjs/penguins-theme-elements15-1.svg){width=100%}
